---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Free Scrabble Solver" description="Our privacy policy: no sign-up, privacy-focused. Your data stays in your browser. Free Scrabble solver with zero personal data collection." keywords="scrabble word finder privacy, privacy-first, no signup, free word finder privacy policy">
  <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-800">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      <span class="text-blue-400">Scrabble</span><span class="text-gray-300">WordsFinder</span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Solver</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Blog</a>
      <a href="/settings" class="hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">⚙️</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We don't collect your personal information. We don't track you. We don't run ads. Your data stays in your browser unless you explicitly choose to back it up.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">No Sign-Up Required</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">ScrabbleWordsFinder.com does not require an account, email address, or any personal information to use. You open the page, you use the solver. That's it.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Data Stored in Your Browser</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We use your browser's localStorage to save:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Your saved/bookmarked words</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Your preferences (dictionary choice, sort order, theme)</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Achievement progress</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>An anonymous UUID (randomly generated, not tied to your identity)</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">This data never leaves your device unless you explicitly opt into server backup.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Anonymous Server Backup</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">If you choose to back up your saved words to our server:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>We store only your word lists tied to a random UUID</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>No email, name, IP address, or other identifying information is stored</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>The UUID is generated locally in your browser — we have no way to connect it to you</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>You can delete this backup at any time from Settings</span></li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">No Third-Party Tracking</h2>
    <div class="border border-purple-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-gray-900/50">
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>We collect anonymous, aggregated usage data to improve features (no personal data)</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>No tracking cookies</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>No ad networks or advertising pixels</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>No social media trackers</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>No fingerprinting or device identification</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">No Data Sold or Shared</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We do not sell, share, trade, or transfer any user data to third parties. Period. We have no data to sell because we don't collect it.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Delete Everything</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">You can nuke all your data at any time:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Go to <a href="/settings" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline underline-offset-2">Settings</a> and click "Delete All Data"</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>This clears your localStorage and removes any server-side backup</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>The action is immediate and irreversible</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-3">🔒 See our full <a href="/terms" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline underline-offset-2">Terms of Use</a> for more details.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your data is handled, reach out at:</p>
    <p class="text-gray-300">Email: <span class="text-blue-400">support@scrabblewordsfinder.com</span></p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Anonymous Usage Insights</h2>
    <div class="border border-blue-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-gray-900/50">
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We track <strong class="text-white">anonymous click events</strong> to understand which features are most used. This helps us prioritise development effort on the tools you actually use.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">What we collect:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Which buttons and links are clicked (e.g., "Solve", "Save Word")</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Page visited at time of click</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Device type (mobile/desktop) and country — derived from IP, not stored individually</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>A random session ID (regenerated each browser session, not linked to you)</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">What we <strong class="text-white">do NOT</strong> collect:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">✗</span><span>Your name, email, or any personally identifiable information</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">✗</span><span>The words you search for or your game results</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">✗</span><span>Cookies that track you across other websites</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-4">This data is used solely to improve ScrabbleWordsFinder. We never sell or share it with third parties.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Opting Out — Turn Off Cookies</h2>
    <div class="border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-gray-900/50">
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">If you prefer not to be tracked at all, you can <strong class="text-white">reject all cookies</strong> via our cookie consent banner (the 🍪 button at the bottom-left) or disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">With cookies disabled or rejected, the following features will be <strong class="text-white">impacted</strong>:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">⚠️</span><span><strong class="text-white">Saved Words won't persist</strong> — your word collection relies on localStorage (linked to your session). Without cookies, we can't identify your session across visits.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">⚠️</span><span><strong class="text-white">Achievements will reset</strong> — progress towards word-finding achievements is stored locally and tied to your anonymous session.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">⚠️</span><span><strong class="text-white">Theme/settings won't be remembered</strong> — your dark mode preference and other settings reset each visit.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">⚠️</span><span><strong class="text-white">Cookie consent banner will reappear</strong> — since we can't store your preference, you'll see the banner on every page load.</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">Features that <strong class="text-white">still work fully</strong> without cookies:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>Word solving — the solver works entirely client-side with no cookies needed</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>Tile probability and rack leave analysis</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>Best opening moves calculator</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>Reference panels (two-letter words, Q without U, rare letters)</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>Blog content and guides</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-4">In short: the core word-finding functionality works perfectly without cookies. Only persistence and personalisation features are affected.</p>
    </div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does ScrabbleWordsFinder collect personal data?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "We collect minimal anonymous data (clicks, country, device type) to improve the site. We do not collect names, emails, or personally identifiable information unless you submit the contact form." } },
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does ScrabbleWordsFinder use cookies?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "We use essential cookies for site functionality and a cookie consent banner. You can opt out of non-essential cookies at any time." } },
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I delete my data?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, you can clear all locally stored data (saved words, preferences) from the Settings page using the \"Nuke localStorage\" button. Contact form submissions can be deleted upon request." } }
  ]
}
</script>
</Layout>
